
Command: skills [ magic | combat | general | casting | adjectives ]

Arguments:
  magic      - shows skills affecting spells
  casting    - shows spell syllabe skills
  combat     - shows skills automatically used in combat
  general    - shows the other non-magical skills

  adjectives - list of skill level adjectives

This command lists you your skills, which you accuire at the various
guilds. Without argument command shows all your skills.

Skill levels shown as bold have been improved by use.

See also 'help skill'.

